extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Grocery Inventory].

  h1 Dynamic Content 

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The Grocery Inventory has the following record counts: 

    ul 
      li #[strong Stores:] !{data.store_count}
      li #[strong Farms:] !{data.farm_count}
      li #[strong Foods:] !{data.food_count}
      li #[strong Food Groups:] !{data.food_group_count}
